{"tid":1499273,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普：美國沒有中国將會更好","createTime":"2019-08-23T16:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T16:42:17.000Z","uid":184679,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7119a167663c81b504fc01d0dc1e3309ac250d96","tid":1499273,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:05:54.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普在社交網站批評中國, 指美國多年來因為中國而損失數以萬億計的金錢, 又指責中國竊取美國的知識產權, 現在也繼續這樣做, 他說不會再容許這個情況發生.        <br />\n<br />\n他又指, 美國過去兩年半, 經濟比中國大幅增長, 並繼續向好, 聲言美國不需要中國, 又指美國沒有中國會過得更好. <br />\n<br />\n特朗普又要求美國企業, 立即開始尋找替代中國的方案, 包括把企業撤回美國, 並在美國生產. 他稍後會對中國加徵關稅作出回應, 形容對美國來說是大好機會.         <br />\n<br />\n另外, 特朗普又說, 已下令所有貨運商, 搜查和拒絕來自中國的類鴉片止痛劑「芬太尼」, 指「芬太尼」每年造成十萬名美國人死亡, 又批評中國國家主席習近平無履行承諾, 處理「芬太尼」的問題.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20190823232817\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20190823232817&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6pggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=a66ffd6b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20190823232817</a>"},{"pid":"3ca8e2beb9dba6b66a0d42622258fbd7a1b3f493","tid":1499273,"uid":52763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:07:01.000Z","msg":"脫勾lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4ed42e8802cdf6a2d66e0099169049553ce126","tid":1499273,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:07:15.000Z","msg":"沙發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28fe3391354e833cb23ebd982e884ea7df03e4c","tid":1499273,"uid":277235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:07:54.000Z","msg":"反面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />砌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開火<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d9ff612f1ac9d7b0609baf693c63366c64ab3c","tid":1